✅ 1. ULTRASONIC SENSOR (HC-SR04)

• VCC → 5V
• GND → GND
• TRIG → D9
• ECHO → D8


---

✅ 2. SERVO MOTOR (SG90)

• Signal (Orange) → D10
• VCC (Red) → 5V
• GND (Brown/Black) → GND


---

✅ 3. HC-05 BLUETOOTH MODULE

• VCC → 5V
• GND → GND
• TXD → D0 (Arduino RX)
• RXD → D1 (Arduino TX)


---

✅ 4. DC GEAR MOTORS (4 Motors)

Motor 1

• Motor1 + → M1+
• Motor1 – → M1−

Motor 2

• Motor2 + → M2+
• Motor2 – → M2−

Motor 3

• Motor3 + → M3+
• Motor3 – → M3−

Motor 4

• Motor4 + → M4+
• Motor4 – → M4−

(If rotation is opposite, swap + and −)


---

✅ 5. BATTERY + SWITCH

• Battery + → Switch → VIN (Motor Power +)
• Battery – → GND


---

✅ 6. COMMON GROUND (IMPORTANT)

• All GND (Bluetooth + Servo + Ultrasonic + Battery − + Arduino) → ONE COMMON GROUND
